const n='---\ntitle: "Cards & Subscriptions"\ndescription: "API endpoints for managing virtual cards (keys) and tracking subscriptions"\n---\n\n# Cards & Subscriptions API\n\nThis section covers the administrative APIs for managing product cards (activation keys) and viewing active subscriptions.\n\n**Note**: All endpoints require Admin Authentication (`/api/admin/*`).\n\n---\n\n## Cards Management\n\n### 1. List Cards\n\nRetrieve a list of all cards (activation keys) in the system, along with their usage status and associated product names.\n\n- **Endpoint**: `/api/admin/cards`\n- **Method**: `GET`\n- **Authentication**: Required (Admin)\n\n#### Success Response (200)\n\n```json\n[\n  {\n    "id": 1,\n    "productId": 3,\n    "productName": "Steam Gift Card $50",\n    "cardNumber": "STEAM-XXXX-YYYY-ZZZZ",\n    "isUsed": false,\n    "orderId": null,\n    "createdAt": "2024-03-21T10:00:00.000Z"\n  }\n]\n```\n\n### 2. Bulk Import Cards\n\nImport multiple cards for a specific `key` type product.\n\n- **Endpoint**: `/api/admin/cards`\n- **Method**: `POST`\n- **Authentication**: Required (Admin)\n\n#### Request Body\n\n```json\n{\n  "productId": 3,\n  "cardNumbers": ["KEY-1234-ABCD", "KEY-5678-EFGH"]\n}\n```\n\n#### Success Response (200)\n\n```json\n{\n  "code": 0,\n  "message": "Successfully added 2 cards"\n}\n```\n\n#### Error Response (400)\n\n```json\n{\n  "statusCode": 400,\n  "message": "Missing required fields"\n}\n```\n\n### 3. Delete Card\n\nDelete an unused card from the system.\n\n- **Endpoint**: `/api/admin/cards/:id`\n- **Method**: `DELETE`\n- **Authentication**: Required (Admin)\n\n#### Success Response (200)\n\n```json\n{\n  "code": 0,\n  "message": "Card deleted successfully"\n}\n```\n\n#### Error Response (400) - Card Used\n\n```json\n{\n  "code": 1,\n  "message": "Cannot delete a card that has already been used"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Subscriptions Management\n\n### 1. List Active Subscriptions\n\nRetrieve a list of all orders that are categorized as subscriptions (status `active` or `expired`).\n\n- **Endpoint**: `/api/admin/subscriptions`\n- **Method**: `GET`\n- **Authentication**: Required (Admin)\n\n#### Success Response (200)\n\n```json\n[\n  {\n    "id": "ORD123456789",\n    "amount": 29.99,\n    "contactEmail": "user@example.com",\n    "status": "active",\n    "createdAt": "2024-03-01T10:00:00.000Z",\n    "paidAt": "2024-03-01T10:05:00.000Z",\n    "metaData": {\n      "subscription_cycle": "1_month",\n      "expire_at": 1711965600000\n    },\n    "productId": 5,\n    "productName": "Pro SaaS Plan",\n    "userId": 42,\n    "userNickname": "John Doe"\n  }\n]\n```\n';export{n as default};
